---
---

<section id="newsletter" class="py-16 md:py-20">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-900/40 to-cyan-900/20 rounded-2xl border border-blue-500/20 p-8 md:p-12 overflow-hidden">
      <!-- Background decorations -->
      <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-blue-500/10 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-48 h-48 bg-cyan-500/10 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>

      <div class="relative max-w-2xl">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 bg-blue-500/10 border border-blue-500/20 rounded-full text-blue-400 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">
          <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
          </svg>
          Newsletter
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-white mb-3">
          Fique por dentro das novidades
        </h2>
        <p class="text-slate-300 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          Receba os melhores artigos sobre DevOps, SRE e Cloud diretamente no seu e-mail. Sem spam, apenas conteúdo relevante.
        </p>

        <form class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 max-w-lg">
          <input
            type="email"
            placeholder="seu@email.com"
            required
            class="flex-1 px-4 py-3 bg-slate-800/80 border border-slate-600 hover:border-blue-500/50 focus:border-blue-500 text-white placeholder-slate-500 rounded-xl outline-none transition-colors text-sm"
          />
          <button
            type="submit"
            class="px-6 py-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-cyan-500 hover:from-blue-500 hover:to-cyan-400 text-white font-semibold rounded-xl transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg shadow-blue-500/25 whitespace-nowrap"
          >
            Inscrever-se
          </button>
        </form>
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-3">
          Ao se inscrever, você concorda com nossa política de privacidade. Cancele a qualquer momento.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
